{
  "title": "Tahti — lab overview",
  "uid": "tahti-overview",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "tags": ["tahti", "app", "monitor.dudeisland.eu"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "environment",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Environment",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
        "query": "label_values(tahti_users_registered_total, environment)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {}
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "API metrics scrape up",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" },
                "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{host}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Registered users",
      "description": "All user accounts (from GET /metrics).",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 0, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "decimals": 0, "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_users_registered_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{environment}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Active users today (UTC)",
      "description": "Distinct users with a new session since UTC midnight.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 0, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "decimals": 0, "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_users_active_today{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{environment}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Load average (1m) — vimage",
      "description": "node_exporter on the lab host (192.168.2.100).",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 0, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "decimals": 2, "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node_load1{instance=\"vimage\"}",
          "legendFormat": "vimage",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "API healthy",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "1": { "text": "HEALTHY", "color": "green" },
                "0": { "text": "UNHEALTHY", "color": "red" }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_api_healthy{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{host}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "HTTP 5xx (last 1h)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 10 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(tahti_http_requests_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",status_class=\"5xx\",environment=~\"$environment\"}[1h])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Audit errors (24h)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "decimals": 0, "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_audit_errors_24h{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{environment}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Stripe webhook failures (total)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "decimals": 0, "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_stripe_webhook_handler_failures_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"} + tahti_stripe_webhook_verify_failures_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "stripe",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "title": "Postgres backup age (hours)",
      "description": "From GET /metrics — newest object under backups/pg/ in MinIO. -1 = unknown.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 1,
          "unit": "h",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "special",
              "options": {
                "match": "null",
                "result": { "text": "N/A", "color": "red" }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 26 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 48 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": "/^-1$/" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "unknown" },
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_postgres_backup_age_hours{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{environment}}",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "HTTP response time (avg, ms)",
      "description": "In-process counter average since API start; resets on deploy.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(tahti_http_request_duration_ms_sum{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}[5m]) / rate(tahti_http_request_duration_ms_count{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "API avg",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "max(tahti_dependency_check_latency_ms{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",dependency=\"postgres\",environment=~\"$environment\"})",
          "legendFormat": "postgres check",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "External probe duration (s)",
      "description": "Blackbox probes from monitor host to lab endpoints.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "s", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds{job=\"tahti_blackbox\",environment=~\"$environment\",probe=~\"health|status|web\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Load average — vimage",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 20, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "node_load1{instance=\"vimage\"}",
          "legendFormat": "1m",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "node_load5{instance=\"vimage\"}",
          "legendFormat": "5m",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "node_load15{instance=\"vimage\"}",
          "legendFormat": "15m",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "title": "HTTP errors by class",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 20, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (status_class) (rate(tahti_http_requests_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{status_class}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "title": "Users over time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 26, "w": 24, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "P501B54A0D5548634" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tahti_users_registered_total{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "registered",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "tahti_users_active_today{job=\"tahti_api_metrics\",environment=~\"$environment\"}",
          "legendFormat": "active today",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "title": "Endpoints monitored",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 32, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Grafana on **monitor.dudeisland.eu** (vimage6) scrapes the **lab stack on vimage** (`192.168.2.100`).\n\n| Source | Metric |\n|--------|--------|\n| `GET /metrics` | Users, deps, HTTP counters, backup age, Stripe webhook failures |\n| `job=node` | Load average (`instance=vimage`) |\n| `job=tahti_blackbox` | External latency + probe up/down |\n\nAlerts: `prometheus-tahti-alerts.yml` (backup >26h WARN, >48h critical). Deploy: `./ops/monitoring/vimage6/deploy.sh`"
      }
    }
  ]
}
